mzDataXMLStruct

Presentation

Internal class, do not use it to store data. Consider using mzData class instead.

Definition

class mzDataXMLStruct(BaseModel):
    metadata : dict
    times : list[float]
    series : Any

How to use

value = mzDataXMLStruct(
    metadata = someDict,
    times = listOfTimes,
    series = series
)

Functions

None

Notes

This is an internal class, it shouldn’t be used to store mz values. This class is automatically populated when parsing a .mzData.xml file and is private.

Consider using mzData class to store your mz and intensities values.
